INFO:
serves warning/information notices to network administrators / NOC / abuse@ if IPs end up in fail2ban.
works with RIPE/ARIN/APNIC & individual abuse@isp.tld whois entries

INSTALL:
- install as root cronjob, running shortly before fail2ban autocleans 
  your fail2ban list (this is variable in the fail2ban config.!)
- done
